summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the 400 Yesler Building; authorizing the execution of a License and Concession Agreement with the Washington State Commission for the Blind providing for the use and occupancy of certain spaces in said building by said Commission and its designated operator(S) for the purpose of operating and maintaining certain vending facilities therein, and also authorizing the execution of a Memorandum of Understanding among the City, said Commission, and the Lessor of said building, regarding the construction, maintenance, and operation of said vending facilities.
